<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-57.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Celebrities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Who is your favorite famous person?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Who is your favorite famous person ? Why ?.
-> I think it is Pham Van Dong, he is one of the greatest historical leader in Viet Nam. He had a charm looks. He leaded local people to protect and build the country. He reminds me of my responsibilites in building and protecting the country.






charm (adj): ấm áp 

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-57.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Celebrities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it hard to be a celebrity?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it hard to be a celebrity?
it is Not entirely.
Because some people who are famous not for their talents but dirty contents attracting a lot of audiences. They are more entertaining. 
While, some celebrity are famous for their talents and professional. It is hard. It requires a lot of time, money, effort and natural ability. 
-> celebrity (n): người nổi tiếng.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-57.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Celebrities</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should they be role models?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should they be role models?
Not entirely.
Because, like i mentioned before, some people use dirty contents to attract the autdiences. i do not support this and i do not think anyone should follow this.
However, with celebrities who are insirping, empowering and have knowledge. i think we should learn from them.
role model (n): tấm gương để noi theo.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-58.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Traditions</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is a special tradition in your family?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is a special tradition in your family?
-> I think my family share similar tradition like other families in my country. We really love our country and put our family first so we worship (thờ cúng) ancestors (tổ tiên) to remind the youth of the sacrifire of the older generation. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-58.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Traditions</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it important to keep traditions?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it important to keep traditions?
Not entirely.
Some good tradition should be protected. for example worshiping ancestors to remind the youth of the older generation sacrifire.
However, some traditions are no longer suitable. It should be changed or canceled. for example, gender bias. People used to prefer boy over girl. We should change this !.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-58.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Traditions</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Have traditions changed?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Have traditions changed?
Yes, of course. 
I see the tradition has changed a lot in a good way. for example, nowadays, all genders are equal in society. In the past, women used to stay at home and take care of the children, do the houseworks but now they are allowed to go to works and earn money like men. They can go to school and vote for president.

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-59.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Wild Animals</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is your favorite wild animal?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite wild (hoang) animal ?
I think it is tiger. because it is the king of animals. It is powerful, strong and independent. I see it like a role model to follow.

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-59.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Wild Animals</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Are zoos good for them?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Are zoos good for them? (Wild Animals)
Not entirely.
Because a lot of animals they do not like to be in 
cage (n): lồng = limited space. They want the freedom to go out and explore the nature. 
However, some anmals are almost endangered because of hunting. So we should protect them.

endangered (adj): tuyệt chủng

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-59.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Wild Animals</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should we protect endangered species?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should we protect endangered (trên đề tuyệt chủng) species ? 
No, i do not think so because it is highly demanding. It requires a lot of money, time and efforts. Government have to invest money to build protecting space for endangered species. While a lot of people who are homeless and in poor condition. I think the government should prioritize there residents.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-60.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Space Travel</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is space travel possible for everyone?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is space travel possible for everyone?
No, of course. It is very expensive. I do not think space travel is available in my country.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-60.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Space Travel</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is the biggest challenge?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the biggest challenge of Space Travel ?
-> I think it is facilities. In my country, space facilities are not developing enough to make  Space Travel tour.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-60.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Space Travel</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should we spend money on space?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should we spend money on space?
-> No, i do not think so it is expensive and impratical. I think the government should invest on facilites, education, healthcare to improve resident's life quality. Many people are poor, hunger and homeless out there.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-61.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Robots</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Will robots replace humans?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Will robots replace humans (people) ?
Not entirely. 
Robot can replace workers in factory (nhà máy), which is not skill demanding. Or simple and repetitive works like cleaning, cooking, ... 
While, people with highly qualified skills and work in creative fields. they can not be replaced.
repetitive (adj): lặp đi lặp 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-61.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Robots</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What can robots do better?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What can robots do better?
I think robot can work for a longer time, it can reduce mistakes. They can perfectly caculate the numbers. 
The company do not have to pay too much money for them.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-61.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Robots</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Are you afraid of robots?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Are you afraid of robots?
I afraid that robot will replace me. Like i mentioned before, robot can not entirely replace human, especially highly skill workers. However, in the future, with ai and advanced robot can collab and replace me.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-62.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Climate Change</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is climate change real?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is climate change (biến đổi khí hậu) real ?
I think it is real because i feel recently the climate has become hotter than ever before and the winter is shorten. The environment is so polluted. 
climate (n): khí hậu</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-62.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Climate Change</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is one way to help?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is one way to help ? Climate Change. 
The government should introduce laws like they ban the motorbikes and invest on public transportation and green energy like solar and wind energy to reduce waste.
While individual/person should turn off the electric equipments when not use. We use public transportation or go walking instead of using motorbikes.   
biến đổi -> do nhiệt độ tăng (xe cộ, điện) 
Chính phủ/ người dân
-> xe cộ (__)
-> năng lượng (gió, mặt trời)

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-62.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Climate Change</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is your city getting hotter?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is your city getting hotter?
Yes, it is. I feel climate is hotter than ever before, especially in the summer. I have to stay at home and turn on the air-contition all day.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-63.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Remote Work</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like working from home?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like working from home?
Not entirely.
Because if i work at home it is time and money saving. i do not have to move to the officers. but at home it is lacking of connection and interaction with my workers.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-63.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Remote Work</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is the biggest distraction?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the biggest distraction ? Remote Work.
I think it is the lacking of superivisor so noone remind me to finish the works. Additionally, working on laptop, there are a lot of distractions on the Internet so it is hard to focus.  

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-63.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Remote Work</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it the future of work?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it the future of work ? Remote Work
I think it might be with officer in the future because offiers work behind the desk so they do not have to communicate and interact with partners and customers so at home can bring similar envrionment.
Additionally, with the help of modern technologies, we have been united. we can make video call, chat and make schedule online easily. 
</p><hr></body></html>